摘要： 必需 | 可选 详细信息： 元素

android.view
注释类型 ViewDebug.IntToString

@Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public static @interface ViewDebug.IntToString

Defines a mapping from an int value to a String. Such a mapping can be used in a @ExportedProperty to provide more meaningful values to the end user.

另请参见：
ViewDebug.ExportedProperty

必需元素摘要
 int from
          The original int value to map to a String.
 String to
          The String to use in place of the original int value.
 

元素详细信息

from

public abstract int from
The original int value to map to a String.

返回：
An arbitrary int value.

to

public abstract String to
The String to use in place of the original int value.

返回：
An arbitrary non-null String.
